fields.description:
We need to add {{sql_confs}} to {{DefineOutput}} in SDP to support following use case

SQL file #1
{code:java}
SET some_conf = some_value;
CREATE STREAMING TABLE st; {code}
SQL file #2
CREATE FLOW INSERT INTO st FROM ....
 
Since we don't store {{sql_confs}} at the Dataset level, the conf would be ignored. We should store it at dataset level and will merge the {{sql_conf}} stored at the dataset level to its corresponding flow when we construct the DataflowGraph.

